dji.sdk.api.media

Class DJIMediaInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.media.DJIMediaInfo

  • public class DJIMediaInfo
extends java.lang.Object

    DJI Phantom 3 Advanced Media Info

    By using this class, developer could parse the information in of the photo. It has functions for getting thumbnail key, thumbnail name, formatting and parsing time.
    Version:
    : V2.4.0
    Author:
    : DJI Software
